# Debug Mode Replacements

*plugin* `debug-mode`

## Replace expression index with expression id.

*Module* `expressions/expression_view` `expressions/image-view` `expressions/table-view` `expressions/text_view` `expressions/folder-view`

*Find*
```js
.createElement(
  'span',
  { class: $DCGView.const('dcg-num') },
  __body__
)
```

*Find* inside `body` => `from`
```js
$this.$model.displayIndex
```

*Replace* `from` with
```js
window.DesModder?.controller?.isPluginEnabled("debug-mode")
  ? $this.$model.id.length <= 6
    ? $this.$model.id
    : $this.$model.id.substring(0, 4) + "â€¦"
  : $this.$model.displayIndex
```
